#features of bus reservation system#
search and reserve seats
system of advance fares, discounts benefits, group offers, round trip plans, special deals, couple offers
payment options, use several payment platforms ad reduce billing expenses, redue duplications, reduce fraud risks
Gps tracking with exact location, departure and estimated arrival times and real time chat for emergency and receive prompt messages with personal attention.
seat selection preference, display visually available seats and allow users to select desired seats 
on-board ticketing where travelers can redeem their ticket, use qr codes to driver to scan and validate ticket for on board ticketing and ticket receipt as redundant copy. use for confirmation of tickets as well as purchasing tickets after boarding.
Business analysis ans report building capability creates reports for ticket sales and cancel reports providing statistics on booking, sales, cancellations for use in specialized intelligence business tools.

